org.dockbox.selene.core.impl.files

Class DefaultConfigurateManager

  • java.lang.Object

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SpongeConfigurateManager

    public abstract class DefaultConfigurateManager
extends DefaultAbstractFileManager
    Implementation of FileManager containing dynamic mapping to appropriate ConfigurationLoaders based on the given FileType by the implementation of this type. Supporting FileType.YAML, FileType.JSON, FileType.XML, FileType.MOD_CONFIG, and FileType.CONFIG file types. Automatically generates, and checks the presence of, files in their directories. For both custom file locations and Extension.id() based.
